		    Cash, Winds of Karana Sheet 1, Broken Lute, and when carrying a weapon, it is ALWAYS Fine Steel
		     &nbsp;
		    </font>
		    </td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td align="middle" width="100%" valign="top" colspan="2"><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Description</font></b>
		    </td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td width="100%" valign="top" colspan="2"><font face="Verdana" size="2">
			The Hermit stays by himself in a remote house out on the plains.  Even though this is not a traditional &quot;Beast&quot;, he is worth good exp. and descent loot.
		  
		  </font>
		  </td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td width="100%" valign="top" colspan="2">
		      <font face="Verdana" size="2">
		      <b>Submitted by:</b> <a href="mailto:azro2000@hotmail.com">Azoa</a></font>
		    </td>
